<div class="info"> -282 +282 </div>
<div class="text ltr">Those who swallow down usury cannot arise except as one whom Shaitan has prostrated by (his) touch does rise. That is because they say, trading is only like usury; and Allah has allowed trading and forbidden usury. To whomsoever then the admonition has come from his Lord, then he desists, he shall have what has already passed, and his affair is in the hands of Allah; and whoever returns (to it)-- these <span class="del">arc</span> <span class="ins">are</span> the inmates of the fire; they shall abide in it.</div>

<div class="info"> -846 +846 </div>
<div class="text ltr">Say: Surely I have manifest proof from my Lord and you call it a lie; I have not with me that which you would hasten; the<span class="del">t</span>  judgment is only Allah's; He relates the truth and He is the best of deciders.</div>

<div class="info"> -1786 +1786 </div>
<div class="text ltr">My Lord! surely they have led many men astray; then whoever follows me, he is surely of me, and whoever disobeys me, Thou surely <span class="del">arc</span> <span class="ins">art</span> Forgiving, Merciful:</div>


<div class="date"> Duplicate lines removed <br/> Fri, 4 Jun 2010 20:00:03 -0400 </div>
